storm','Magma Storm','fire','special',100,75,5,5,0,'selected-pokemon',100,'Prevents the target from fleeing and inflicts damage for 2-5 turns.','Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. Rapid Spin cancels this effect.',4,0,0,NULL),(464,'dark-void','Dark Void','dark','status',NULL,50,10,10,0,'all-opponents',NULL,'Puts the target to sleep.','Puts the target to sleep.',4,0,0,NULL),(465,'seed-flare','Seed Flare','grass','special',120,85,5,5,0,'selected-pokemon',40,'Has a chance to lower the target’s Special Defense by two stages.','Inflicts regular damage. Has a chance to lower the target’s Special Defense by two stages.',4,0,0,NULL),(466,'ominous-wind','Ominous Wind','ghost','special',60,100,5,5,0,'selected-pokemon',10,'Has a chance to raise all of the user’s stats by one stage.','Inflicts regular damage. Has a chance to raise all of the user’s stats one stage.',4,0,0,NULL),(467,'shadow-force','Shadow Force','ghost','physical',120,100,5,5,0,'selected-pokemon',NULL,'User vanishes, dodging all attacks, and hits next turn. Hits through Protect and Detect.','Inflicts regular damage. User vanishes for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. This move ignores the effects of Detect and Protect. This move cannot be selected by Sleep Talk.',4,0,0,NULL),(468,'hone-claws','Hone Claws','dark','status',NULL,NULL,15,15,0,'user',NULL,'Raises the user’s Attack and accuracy by one stage.','Raises the user’s Attack and accuracy by one stage.',5,0,0,NULL),(469,'wide-guard','Wide Guard','rock','status',NULL,NULL,10,10,3,'users-field',NULL,'Prevents any multi-target moves from hitting friendly Pokémon this turn.','Moves with multiple targets will not