turn to \"recharge\", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.',3,0,0,NULL),(10014,'shadow-hold','Shadow Hold','shadow','status',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'opponents-field',NULL,'Prevents the target from leaving battle.','The target cannot switch out normally. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This effect ends when the user leaves the field. The target may still escape by using Baton Pass, U-turn, or a Shed Shell. Both the user and the target pass on this effect with Baton Pass.',3,0,0,NULL),(10015,'shadow-mist','Shadow Mist','shadow','status',NULL,100,0,0,0,'opponents-field',NULL,'Lowers the target’s evasion by two stages.','Lowers the target’s evasion by two stages.',3,0,0,NULL),(10016,'shadow-panic','Shadow Panic','shadow','status',NULL,90,0,0,0,'opponents-field',NULL,'Confuses the target.','Confuses the target.',3,0,0,NULL),(10017,'shadow-shed','Shadow Shed','shadow','status',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'entire-field',NULL,'Removes Light Screen, Reflect, and Safeguard.','Removes the effects of Light Screen, Reflect, and Safeguard.',3,0,0,NULL),(10018,'shadow-sky','Shadow Sky','shadow','status',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,'entire-field',NULL,'Changes the weather to Shadow Sky for five turns.','Changes the weather to Shadow Sky for five turns. Pokémon other than Shadow Pokémon take 1/16 their max HP at the end of every turn. This move is typeless for the purposes of Weather Ball.',3,0,0,NULL);
